Title : Meu Pé de Laranja Lima (TV series)
Text : '''''Meu Pé de Laranja Lima''''' (''My Sweet Orange Tree'') is a 1998 Brazilian [[telenovela]], based on the [[Meu Pé de Laranja Lima|novel of the same name]].

